rows.title: Harem Builder
rows.titleText:
You were randomly selected by the shut-in lottery#3394 to get reincarnated in the fantasy world of Krion.

You will be born in the nobility of Crobalt Empire as the only son and heir of Marquis Kradger and will live without any struggles and die happily without ever experiencing poverty.

With the below interface you can pick people to be a part of your harem. These people are famous 'characters' from things called 'Animes'.

You will meet them randomly and the amount you can pick is limited, some worlds have conflicting signatures so picking only one of them is allowed, and some characters may also conflict and only one can be picked.

A part of their appearance may also change due to the internet dimensional travel, while it won't be much it might still be noticeable enough for some.

All of them will have custom personalities and will not have any memories of their original world.

Now go and build your dream harem.

rows.title: Size
rows.titleText:
How big is your harem?
Basically how many characters you can pick.

objects.title: Nami
objects.text:
She works at the Graycon ship company and was asigned to your ship on a trip of yours.
You befriended her and employed her as your maid and she later made her way into your harem.
She is aloof and very greedy.
She is also a sub who is very shy when matters about sex are brought up.

objects.title: Nico Robin
objects.text:
She works at the Graycon ship company and was asigned to your ship on a trip of yours.
You befriended her and employed her as your maid and she later made her way into your harem.
She is mature and graceful, a air of dignity always surrounds her.
She is also a Dom and is very teasing, she often teases you and other members all as a front to get them aroused.

objects.title: Boa Hancock
objects.text:
On a visit of yours to a nature resort you met her, she is a native there and is very well respected there.
You helped her there with some troubles and to repay you she became your personal advisor.
She is a switch who blushes a lot around and is clearly obsessed with you and all of your possessions and will go to extreme lengths to make sure it stays like that.

objects.title: Yamato
objects.text:
She is from a special race and came to  The Siphor Academy for Nobles in the third semester of the first year as a part of the student exchange programme.
You and her quickly became friends and later became much closer.
She is a Dom who is proficient in fighting and will use her strength to overpower you while fucking to show dominance.

objects.title: Hinata
objects.text:
After you first semester at Siphor academy while returning to your home you stayed in a village for some time and she attended to you there.
Impressed from by her you offered her to become the first maid among your personal servants and she accepted whole heartedly.
She is a sub with a kind personality and is very caring towards you and almost anyone who she meets.

objects.title: Sakura
objects.text:
After you first semester at Siphor academy while returning to your home you stayed in a village for some time and she attended to you there.
Impressed from by her you offered her to become the first maid among your personal servants and she accepted whole heartedly.
She is a sub with a brash personality but is very mature and works to improve herself and on her mistakes.

objects.title: Tsunade
objects.text:
In the village you stayed at while returning back she was the ex-chief.
Retired and bored from the life there she was looking to venture out.
You became close with her in the time that you stayed there and agreed to take her as your Guardian.
She is a switch and is very aloof, she likes gambling and wastes away hours gambling her heart out and it brings her joy.

objects.title: Yoruichi
objects.text:
She is the daughter of Count Balcreto and your classmate at the Siphor Academy for Nobles.
You became friends with her and were very competitive with her at the start but after the first semester you accepted defeat but became close companion with her.
She is a Dom and is likes cats a lot and will sometimes make you dress and act as one while around her.

objects.title: Orihime
objects.text:
She is a friend of your cousin and you met her when visiting them for a ball held in their land.
You became close with her but had to leave. Some years after this you met her again but this time you kept in touch and kept meeting at times, after graduating from the Academy you finally decided to own up to your feelings and got them returned in full.
She is a Sub and is a very kind person who likes to take care of the people she is on good terms with.

objects.title: Rukia
objects.text:
She used to bully you when you were younger and later found you to apologize and reflect on her doings.
You forgave her and became extremely close friends later on.
She is a Sub with a brash personality and while she doesn't show it, she does care a bit for the people around her.

objects.title: Nelliel
objects.text:
You didn't know her exactly but one day she came up to you and admitted her feelings for you, to not let her down you agreed to be friends with her.
She is a Switch who is very free spirited and aloof.
While very childish sometimes she can become extremely serious and can be relied upon.

objects.title: Rangiku
objects.text:
She is a teacher at the Siphor Academy for Nobles and was your Homeroom teacher in the Siphor Academy.
Starting as a student and teacher your relationship developed further and at the end you got with her with the pretense of her being your personal tutor.
She is a Dom but is very light hearted and likes to joke around with everyone and especially you.

objects.title: Rias
objects.text:
She is from the noble bloodline of a different high ranking race and says that she comes from a different world.
She is also a very important student at the Siphor Academy and is treated with respect by teachers and the director even, and is feared and respected by even the Emperor of Crobalt Empire.
You caught her eye with your performance and she demanded for you to become her servant but later became her partner.
She is a Dom and her charms are otherworldly, she is authoritarian and demands respect from all your subjects and you even.

objects.title: Akeno
objects.text:
She is a well respected senior student in the Siphor Academy and a senior of yours.
She is known for her competence and is said to be from a foreign race.
She is a Switch with a calm and collected demeanor, she is a charmer and often uses them to get her stuff done.

objects.title: Asia
objects.text:
She is a rookie nun in the church near the siphor academy, you met with her multiple times when visiting there and slowly became well acquainted with her.
She is a Sub with a innocent personality and she is slow on uptake of intimate topics and is extremely reliant on you.

objects.title: Xenovia
objects.text:
She is a knight in the elite squad of the armt of the Marquis Kradger (your father). Because of her competence and excllence she was assigned to you as your personal guard.
As you two stayed together for a long time you developed an agreement with her to satisfy eachother's needs which later evolved into something more romantic.
She is a Dom and considers herself superior to others because of her superior strength but is very protective of you.

rows.title: Akame Ga Kill
rows.titleText: Select Waifus from Akame Ga Kill

objects.title: Akame
objects.text:
During a Academy Trip you went to a different country, there you discovered a war going on between the Nation's army and a Rebel force.
After observing the situation there you decide to side with the Rebel Forces and go to meet them.
at their headquarters you meet Akame, the strongest warrior among the rebels.
As you are helping them you grow close with her as a companion and develop an intimate relationship with her as partners.
After the conflict is resolved you ask her to be enrolled at the academy and be classmates there.
She is a Dom but is obsessive and caring, she watches over you and helps you while still maintaining a power dynamic.

objects.title: Esdeath
objects.text:
During a Academy Trip you went to a different country, there you discovered a war going on between the Nation's army and a Rebel force.
After observing the situation there you decide to side with the Nation's army.
At the military camp you meet Esdeath, the commander of the army and the strongest soldier there.
You assist her as her aid and become close with her as partners.
After the war is over she becomes a war strategy and Fighting Teacher at the Siphor Academy.
She uses the excuse of extra lessons to meet with you more in the Academy and you grow even closer.
She is a Sadistic Dom into extreme kinks and is a master of putting people in their place.
She lives to be the one in charge and have authority and command over everything that she can.

objects.title: Chelsea
objects.text:
When visiting a foreign nation for an Academy trip you meet her there.
She was your group's guide there who assisted you there.
After spending some time with her you started liking her and offered her a high ranking job in your marquessate and she agreed.
She slowly started trusting you and you two spent a lot of time together whenever you visited home.
She is a Sub who is extremely grateful to you and thinks very highly of you.
She is friendly, selfless and treats others with respect.

objects.title: Mikasa
objects.text:
She is a high ranking officer of the Police in your marquessate, you have met her a couple of times at parties and she also trained you in fighting before you left for the Siphor academy.
Whenever you come back she takes a test to see how much you've grown.
She is a Sub who is obsessed with you and extremely over protective, she will kill even civilians if it was necessary for your safety.

objects.title: Annie
objects.text:
She is a Rookie police force member in your marquessate.
She is the direct aid of a high ranking officer and hence has met you multiple times.
She was a competitor of your while in training but soon surpassed you but still remained close.
She is a Sub who pretends to hate you on face value but actually loves you a lot but does not show it.

objects.title: Historia
objects.text:
She is rumored to be from a special bloodline and was enslaved for the same reason.
You pitied her and bought her to be appointed as your servant, and she has been with you since.
She is a masochistic sub who likes to be treated roughly and thinks of that as a sign of affection and is grateful when such is done to her.

rows.title: Choose a Queen
rows.titleText:
As you will be the king of the harem, pick a member to be the queen, she will also be your wife and everyone else will be a concubine.

Only the characters that are a member of the harem can be selected as a Queen.

Some characters aren't suitable to be a queen and hence will not be present in the list.

objects.title: Nico Robin
objects.text: As the queen she will make it that evryone is educated properly about how to handle themselves and she will be kind to other members.

objects.title: Boa Hancock
objects.text: She will be even more obsessed with you and will be hesistant towards sharing you with others but will eventually give in, she will make sure that everyone is dressed as per your taste.

objects.title: Yamato
objects.text: She will make everyone learn how to fight and while allowing sharing it can only happen with her overseeing the other girls who participate.

objects.title: Hinata
objects.text: She will be kind and caring towards everyone treating them with respect and love and will be extremely understanding.

objects.title: Tsunade
objects.text: She will barely care anout the other stuff but will make everyone participate in gambling.

objects.title: Yoruichi
objects.text:
She will command some authority over every other member and will make everyone dress as cats always.
She will only allow others if she herself is satisfied.

objects.title: Orihime
objects.text: She will only be the queen in name and won't force others to do much.

objects.title: Rukia
objects.text: She will make sure a strict code of conduct is established but won't interfere in anything else.

objects.title: Rangiku
objects.text: She will make others follow her orders on some things but will allow free reign to everyone else.

objects.title: Rias
objects.text:
She will take full authority over everyone and even you, wile you will be the target of everyone's affection she will be the authority figure and you will only ever be second to her in that aspect.
She will govern every little thing that each member and you do.
While she will mostly use you to enjoy herself she will sometimes allow others to join in but even then her satisfaction would be of the utmost priority.

objects.title: Akeno
objects.text:
She will be a bit teasing about others sharing you but won't mind it.
She will be kind and compassionate towards others and will protect and care for them.

objects.title: Xenovia
objects.text:
She will make it a rule that she comes first but after she is satisfied won't care about what you do with others.
She will act like an older sister to others and will keep their well being in mind.

objects.title: Akame
objects.text: She will keep the enviroment competitive and will make sure no one can horde you, instead will allow everyone a equal chance.

objects.title: Esdeath
objects.text:
She will be full authoritarian Queen and will impose strict rules on everyone, limiting most things that they can do.
She will mostly hoard you to herself and will occasionally allow some girls access but it would be based on their competence in tests taken by her in which she will test their body to the limits with torture and some kinkplay.

objects.title: Mikasa
objects.text: She will be extremely obsessive and will only allow others after some convincing, but if anyone approaches you unnecessarily she will shoo them off.

objects.title: Annie
objects.text: She will not take any authority and will let it stay as a free for all.

objects.title: No Queen
objects.text: There will be no queen, and all of them will have equal status.

rows.title: An Exotic Arangement
rows.titleText:
[Hidden bonus #1]
As you picked an Important figure of their as the Queen you can have a special arrangement with the exotic tribe.
As an additional benefit you get sent someone from the tribe to be your servant and a part of your harem once every year

objects.title: Alliance
objects.text: You form an alliance with them, entailing that you will aid them with military help while they will give you consessions on all raw material they export.

objects.title: Vassal State
objects.text: As their current situation has become very bad, to protect themselves they are willing to sign a vassal state contract with them.

rows.title: Political Marriage
rows.titleText:
As you married the daughter of another noble you can get into an alliance with them.
As an additional benefit you get sent someone from the County to be your servant and a part of your harem once every month.

objects.title: Choice
objects.text: The County of Balcreto and The Marquessate of Kradger enter into an alliance becoming close allies.

objects.title: Choice
objects.text: as the both of you are the only heirs the County and the Marquessate unite to become one and are promoted to the level of a Duke by the Emperor.

rows.title: Military Marriage
rows.titleText:
You married the commander of the strongest military force, and are able to control them and the military controlled nation that they are a part of.
As an additional benefit you get sent someone from their Nation to be your servant and a part of your harem once every week.

objects.title: Alliance
objects.text:
You enter an alliance entailing you helping that military with manufactured goods and some raw materials in return for their military support.
Support from a force of such scale solidifies your status in the Empire and makes you respected by the other nobles.

objects.title: Take Over
objects.text:
Instead of forming an alliance you absorb the military force and the small nation into your marquessate.
Having such a force under you makes all the nobles of the empire fear you and for even the emperor to show you proper respect.

rows.title: Otherworldly Alliance
rows.titleText:
You married the princess of the underworld and got acquainted with them.
Impressed by you they give you some options to choose from:
No matter what choice you pick a new demon will be sent to be your personal caretaker everyday, and you and other harem members of yours will get turned into immortal and unaging demons just like your wife.

objects.title: Alliance
objects.text: You form an alliance with them, supplying them with animals, gold and precious jewels in return for their support with demonic magic, curse and the rest.

objects.title: Backer
objects.text:
Instead of an alliance they will become your backer supplying you with such and more to aid you in conquering the empire and becoming its emperor, but you will have to establish places for them to be worshiped by the citizens of the empire and they will take a cut of the tax and whatever money you gain by any sources.
They will also take a cut from whatever is found in the treasury of the previous emperor.

objects.title: Vassal State
objects.text:
You can also make your marquessate a vassal of the underworld.
You will get a lot of support from them but in turn will have to pay taxes to them and they will appoint a demon over you to whom you will have to report and from whom you have to get permission before taking any decisions, consequently the appointed one can strongly 'suggest' policies to be applied.

objects.title: Part of the Underworld
objects.text:
The final choice is to surrender your marquessate to the Underworld, you will no longer be its owner and it will become their place to rule, they in turn will give you a large estate in the underworld with all the staff that you will ever need and you will also get an allowance by them which is a part of what profit they can get from your previous marquessate.
This way you can spend an eternity enjoying yourself with your harem and will not ever have to worry about anything.

rows.title: Congratulations!
rows.titleText: Congratulations on creating your harem, now go enjoy with all these beautiful ladies.

defaultRowText: This is a row, and inside of it, you can place choices. On both rows and choices Requirements can be placed, which will block a row from being viewed, or make the player unable to select a choice, depending on either Point-types or the Ids of other choices. Point-types can be made in Features then Manage Points. Hovering over buttons will explain what they do. The Design of the project can be changed in 'Modify Design' at the side navigation bar, and private styling for each row can be turned on in the rows Settings. Default text like this can be turned off in Features -> Manage Defaults.
defaultChoiceText: This is a Choice, and inside of it, you can place images and text. Scores can be added to it, and have Point-types attached. Addons can be added underneath the image and text. In the Functions at the bottom of the choice, there is an array of different things that can be done. Default text like this can be turned off in Features then Manage Defaults.
